11#ifndef PC_SCTP_TRANSPORT_H_
12#define PC_SCTP_TRANSPORT_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/dtls_transport_interface.h"
17#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
18#include "api/sctp_transport_interface.h"
19#include "media/sctp/sctp_transport_internal.h"
20#include "p2p/base/dtls_transport_internal.h"
21#include "pc/dtls_transport.h"
22#include "rtc_base/third_party/sigslot/sigslot.h"
23#include "rtc_base/thread.h"
24#include "rtc_base/thread_annotations.h"
25
26namespace webrtc {
27
28// This implementation wraps a cricket::SctpTransport, and takes
29// ownership of it.
30// This object must be constructed and updated on the networking thread,
31// the same thread as the one the cricket::SctpTransportInternal object
32// lives on.
33class SctpTransport : public SctpTransportInterface,
34 public sigslot::has_slots<> {
35 public:
36 explicit SctpTransport(
37 std::unique_ptr<cricket::SctpTransportInternal> internal);
38
39 rtc::scoped_refptr<DtlsTransportInterface> dtls_transport() const override;
40 SctpTransportInformation Information() const override;
41 void RegisterObserver(SctpTransportObserverInterface* observer) override;
42 void UnregisterObserver() override;
43
44 // Internal functions
45 void Clear();
46 void SetDtlsTransport(rtc::scoped_refptr<DtlsTransport>);
47 // Initialize the cricket::SctpTransport. This can be called from
48 // the signaling thread.
49 void Start(int local_port, int remote_port, int max_message_size);
50
51 // TODO(https://bugs.webrtc.org/10629): Move functions that need
52 // internal() to be functions on the webrtc::SctpTransport interface,
53 // and make the internal() function private.
54 cricket::SctpTransportInternal* internal() {
55 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
56 return internal_sctp_transport_.get();
57 }
58
59 const cricket::SctpTransportInternal* internal() const {
60 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(owner_thread_);
61 return internal_sctp_transport_.get();
62 }
63
64 protected:
65 ~SctpTransport() override;
66
67 private:
68 void UpdateInformation(SctpTransportState state);
69 void OnInternalReadyToSendData();
70 void OnAssociationChangeCommunicationUp();
71 void OnInternalClosingProcedureStartedRemotely(int sid);
72 void OnInternalClosingProcedureComplete(int sid);
73 void OnDtlsStateChange(cricket::DtlsTransportInternal* transport,
74 cricket::DtlsTransportState state);
75
76 // NOTE: |owner_thread_| is the thread that the SctpTransport object is
77 // constructed on. In the context of PeerConnection, it's the network thread.
78 rtc::Thread* const owner_thread_;
79 SctpTransportInformation info_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(owner_thread_);
80 std::unique_ptr<cricket::SctpTransportInternal> internal_sctp_transport_
81 RTC_GUARDED_BY(owner_thread_);
82 SctpTransportObserverInterface* observer_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(owner_thread_) =
83 nullptr;
84 rtc::scoped_refptr<DtlsTransport> dtls_transport_
85 RTC_GUARDED_BY(owner_thread_);
86};
87
88} // namespace webrtc
89#endif // PC_SCTP_TRANSPORT_H_
